---
title: "Update following list (Subscriber)"
---
flowchart TD
    A([Subscriber wants to change who they follow]) --> B[/Selects a new list of producers to follow/]
    B --> C{User is a Subscriber?}
    C -- No --> D([Rejected — must have Subscriber role])
    C -- Yes --> E[Old following list is replaced with new selection]
    E --> F([Following list updated — feed will reflect changes])
